name: Key to my Heart Necklace
description:
This necklace is ideal for those who love love :) Like me.

*Makes a great pair with a suit jacket.

*In between the chain there are beads that change color when the light reflects them (purple, green, blue..)

*The pendant is made of a key which has chain wrapped around it and a heart with a key hole in it hanging down with my logo "Made With Love".

name: Music Notes Bottle Cap Earrings
description:
Ideal for the music lover! Would be a great gift for your music teacher.

*These are made out of beer caps but are covered with paper on the inside and outside of the cap.

*The inside is covered with a glossy sticker to give it a shine.

*Paper is on the outside as well to cover up the beer logo.

name: Wooden Beaded Flower Bracelet
description:
Ideal for the girly girl! Would make a good summertime/springtime bracelet.

*This bracelet has beads that are pretty pastel colors and are spaced out by honeycomb spacers to separate them.

*Lightweight.

*You can wear it with pretty much anything!

name: Guitar Pick Earrings
description:
Ideal for the guitar player! Makes a great gift for an aspiring musician.

*They come in different colors such as blue, green, etc.

*CUSTOMIZE! Ask for a certain color and I'll see what I can do.

*Lightweight.

name: Bottle Cap Earrings
description:
Ideal for any partier! These would also make a great gift to a friend who is a bartender.

*Caps come in all different brands such as- Budweiser, Bud Light, Heineken, Corona, Sam Adams etc. 

*IBC Root Beer caps are available as well.

*CUSTOMIZE! Let me know what kind of cap you want and I can tell you if I have it and I can make you a custom order.
